law.text: In each judicial district there shall be a court-designated worker or agency. The number of persons assigned as court-designated workers shall be determined by the Administrative Office of the Courts.
law.history: Created 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 423, sec. 4, effective July 1, 1987.
